comments: Brown (BOS) places his arm on Beal's (WAS) body and the contact does not affect his FOM.
Horford (BOS) makes marginal contact to Harrell's (WAS) arm during the gather of his driving shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) does not beat Brown (BOS) to the spot on his driving shot attempt. Marginal contact occurs as the two players come together during the drive.
Schroder (BOS) makes contact to Dinwiddie's (WAS) arm during the drive that does not affect his SBQR.
Schroder (BOS) puts his hands vertical and makes marginal contact to Dinwiddie's (WAS) body that does not affect his shot attempt near the rim.
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Dinwiddie (WAS).
Horford (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Kuzma (WAS) and contact is marginal.
Smart (BOS) makes contact to Beal's (WAS) body during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Beal (WAS) engages with Brown (BOS) and makes marginal contact that does not affect his ability to rebound.
Schroder (BOS) makes contact to Dinwiddie's (WAS) arm that affects his SBQR.
